1
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:40,850
[Fated Hearts]

2
00:01:46,550 --> 00:01:49,009
[Episode 34]

3
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,100
[In Reverence, Song Cheng]

4
00:01:55,780 --> 00:01:57,830
[Memorial Tablet of My Friend, Li Hu]
[Memorial Tablet of My Friend, Chen San]

5
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,220
The First Prince I knew

6
00:01:57,479 --> 00:01:58,940
was a loyal and righteous man.

7
00:01:57,850 --> 00:02:00,350
[Memorial Tablet of My Friend, Gu Yu]
[Memorial Tablet of My Friend, Hound]

8
00:01:59,070 --> 00:02:01,270
There's no way you'd ever plot treason.

9
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:03,229
You must have been framed.

10
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,370
So I secretly investigated

11
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:06,480
and found

12
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,010
the bodies of our brothers.

13
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,710
I buried them quietly.

14
00:02:10,610 --> 00:02:12,790
[Memorial Tablet of My Friend, Gu Yu]
[Memorial Tablet of My Friend, Hound]

15
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:14,030
Before we avenge them,

16
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:17,630
we have to swallow

17
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:19,290
all the tears and bitterness.

18
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,470
Our brothers are
still watching us from above.

19
00:02:21,470 --> 00:02:22,280
Your Highness,

20
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,540
leave Murong Jie to me.

21
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,079
I swear

22
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:26,810
I'll take his damn head myself!

23
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:30,150
Good.

24
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,400
The Murong father and son
framed Feng Suige.

25
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,860
They won't spare
the Feng Battalion either.

26
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:36,490
The Feng Battalion

27
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,190
has already been controlled by Murong Yao.

28
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:39,120
Impossible.

29
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:41,590
Everyone in the Feng Battalion
has fought side by side with us.

30
00:02:41,590 --> 00:02:43,520
They'd never betray His Highness.

31
00:02:43,630 --> 00:02:45,890
Anyone who refused to yield to Murong Yao

32
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,280
was killed by him.

33
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,280
I pledged my loyalty to Your Highness

34
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,870
and refused to serve under Murong Yao,

35
00:02:52,870 --> 00:02:53,680
so I

36
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,560
retired early.

37
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,680
Now I'm just a commoner.

38
00:02:57,590 --> 00:02:58,450
Your Highness,

39
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,360
we've been

40
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,420
searching for you.

41
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,950
Such a huge upheaval in Susha

42
00:03:04,750 --> 00:03:06,480
must have raised suspicions.

43
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:07,360
The entire court

44
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,360
is controlled by the Murong family.

45
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:11,190
No one dares to question this matter.

46
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:13,110
However, during my investigation,

47
00:03:13,110 --> 00:03:13,710
I found someone

48
00:03:13,710 --> 00:03:15,310
secretly looking into this.

49
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,280
It's Shen Wu,

50
00:03:17,810 --> 00:03:18,840
the Minister of Rites.

51
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:21,020
Shen Wu is an opportunist.

52
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:23,590
He definitely didn't want
to investigate it himself.

53
00:03:23,590 --> 00:03:25,650
Someone must be pulling his strings.

54
00:03:26,630 --> 00:03:27,910
The Murong father and son
and Empress Zhuang

55
00:03:27,910 --> 00:03:28,990
all know the truth.

56
00:03:29,470 --> 00:03:31,030
They're too busy concealing it

57
00:03:31,030 --> 00:03:31,960
to investigate.

58
00:03:32,190 --> 00:03:32,680
So,

59
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,730
there's only one person

60
00:03:34,730 --> 00:03:35,960
with such power and the desire

61
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:36,960
to know the truth.

62
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:40,560
Chengyang.

63
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:42,090
Song Cheng,

64
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:43,910
I want to meet Shen Wu.

65
00:03:44,030 --> 00:03:44,890
Can you help me?

66
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,020
No problem.

67
00:03:50,650 --> 00:03:52,620
[Memorial Tablet of My Friend, Li Hu]
[Memorial Tablet of My Friend, Chen San]

68
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:52,430
Brothers,

69
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,560
I swear

70
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:59,829
I'll make them pay for blood with blood.

71
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,630
Mother, you've come at a good time.

72
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:57,010
The lamb chop from Susha

73
00:04:57,130 --> 00:04:58,590
is incredibly delicious.

74
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:00,670
Everyone out!

75
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,020
-Yes.
-Yes.

76
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,120
Stop.

77
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:07,160
Mother, just say what you want to say.

78
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,820
If they dare to breathe a word,

79
00:05:08,830 --> 00:05:09,690
just kill them.

80
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,850
I know why you've come, Mother.

81
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,840
Bring it here.

82
00:05:39,850 --> 00:05:40,560
Mother, can you tell

83
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,760
whose hamlet this is?

84
00:05:42,390 --> 00:05:43,390
It's Liang Pin's.

85
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,060
How could you kill him?

86
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,140
I am the Emperor.

87
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,680
What's wrong with me killing Liang Pin?

88
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,270
He was the Imperial Military Commander!

89
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,200
What commander?

90
00:05:54,590 --> 00:05:56,010
Wasn't he just your dog?

91
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,390
Mother,

92
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,480
you tried to kill my woman.

93
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:00,540
So what if I killed your dog in return?

94
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:05,490
He was not even as good as a dog.

95
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,490
Calling him that

96
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:08,300
insults dogs.

97
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:12,160
Princess Xiyang arrives!

98
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,580
Greetings, Empress Dowager.

99
00:06:34,870 --> 00:06:35,430
Xiyang.

100
00:06:36,270 --> 00:06:36,720
Come.

101
00:06:46,220 --> 00:06:47,720
This is the lamb chop from Susha—

102
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:48,720
quite delicious.

103
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,650
I'll cut a piece for you myself.

104
00:06:50,650 --> 00:06:51,450
Your Majesty,

105
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:54,220
why are you protecting this bitch

106
00:06:54,310 --> 00:06:55,180
like this?

107
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:55,720
Here.

108
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:00,800
How does it taste?

109
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:06,070
It seems you're determined

110
00:07:06,070 --> 00:07:07,390
to go against me.

111
00:07:07,870 --> 00:07:08,510
Great.

112
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,370
My Jingyan has grown up.

113
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,090
You raised me well, Mother.

114
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,220
How about this?

115
00:07:15,950 --> 00:07:17,410
Go enjoy your golden years

116
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:19,290
and stay out of state affairs.

117
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,730
I wouldn't dare.

118
00:07:22,390 --> 00:07:24,100
I'm afraid you'll ruin Jinxiu

119
00:07:24,270 --> 00:07:26,110
for this cheap Susha woman.

120
00:07:26,430 --> 00:07:28,560
Mother, you really care about Jinxiu.

121
00:07:31,770 --> 00:07:33,050
But this is my kingdom.

122
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,240
I can ruin it however I want!

123
00:07:35,650 --> 00:07:37,190
You always say I'm incompetent,

124
00:07:37,190 --> 00:07:39,070
but that's because
you can't see my talent.

125
00:07:39,070 --> 00:07:39,930
What I'm good at

126
00:07:40,159 --> 00:07:41,490
isn't ruling a kingdom.

127
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:42,950
It's destroying one.

128
00:07:45,820 --> 00:07:46,950
Liang Pin was the first

129
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:48,370
to dare kill my woman.

130
00:07:48,950 --> 00:07:49,800
I hope

131
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:52,200
he's the last.

132
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:57,310
Empress Dowager,

133
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:58,950
please have some tea.

134
00:08:21,870 --> 00:08:22,930
Mother, calm down.

135
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,920
Please take care of your health.

136
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:43,679
If you're truly a filial son,

137
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:46,039
get rid of Feng Xiyang for me.

138
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:55,740
Whether you're truly filial as a son,

139
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,480
we'll see by what you do.

140
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,890
I can't stand

141
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,930
that bitch Feng Xiyang any longer.

142
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:09,390
Mother,

143
00:09:09,870 --> 00:09:10,670
I understand.

144
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:29,550
[Linfang Hall]

145
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:45,030
Princess, you're here all alone.

146
00:09:45,030 --> 00:09:46,720
You must be troubled and have come here

147
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:47,780
to clear your mind.

148
00:09:56,130 --> 00:09:56,960
Prince of Zhennan,

149
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,160
you must hate my guts.

150
00:09:59,150 --> 00:10:00,240
All this concern

151
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,270
and polite talk…

152
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:03,130
what are you plotting now?

153
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,570
Why would I hate you?

154
00:10:12,670 --> 00:10:14,070
There's no one else here.

155
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:15,900
Why ask what you already know?

156
00:10:16,510 --> 00:10:18,310
Bai Shouzhuo died because of me.

157
00:10:19,030 --> 00:10:20,290
Shouldn't you hate me?

158
00:10:22,870 --> 00:10:24,910
Why do I see

159
00:10:25,820 --> 00:10:27,500
hostility in your eyes?

160
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:29,610
The eyes see what the mind thinks.

161
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:30,840
What's on your mind

162
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,530
is what you see with your eyes.

163
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,880
If you view me as an enemy,

164
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,930
of course you'll sense hostility.

165
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:39,070
You make a good point.

166
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:40,960
But tell me,

167
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,840
how have we ended up

168
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,210
as enemies?

169
00:10:46,870 --> 00:10:47,850
You forgot?

170
00:10:48,510 --> 00:10:50,170
The first time we met,

171
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:52,150
we were already enemies.

172
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:57,160
Thank you for reminding me.

173
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,230
Since

174
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,480
we've been enemies all along,

175
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,310
I feel much better.

176
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,580
Are you here to kill me?

177
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:15,120
Yes.

178
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:18,040
Then why haven't you done it yet?

179
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:22,530
Because I still owe you a favor.

180
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:24,060
Someone like you

181
00:11:24,330 --> 00:11:25,860
actually cares about that?

182
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,250
Because I'm hypocritical enough.

183
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,240
That's actually

184
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,960
the most honest thing I've heard from you.

185
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:31,600
So,

186
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:33,470
since I'm being honest for once,

187
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:34,720
let me give you

188
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:36,300
one last piece of advice.

189
00:11:40,300 --> 00:11:41,300
Leave this place.

190
00:11:42,130 --> 00:11:43,080
I can help you.

191
00:11:44,870 --> 00:11:45,750
Xia Jingshi,

192
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:49,650
don't tell me
you want me to turn back now?

193
00:11:50,030 --> 00:11:50,890
Feng Xiyang,

194
00:11:52,030 --> 00:11:52,840
no one in this world

195
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,150
understands what you're thinking

196
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:55,450
better than I do.

197
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:57,510
Because I've walked every step

198
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:59,040
of the path you're walking.

199
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:00,880
Your facade,

200
00:12:01,750 --> 00:12:02,610
your despair,

201
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:05,920
and your desperate gamble—
I understand them all.

202
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:07,710
After my father died,

203
00:12:08,750 --> 00:12:10,150
I just wanted to survive.

204
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:13,200
Is it wrong for someone
to just want to live?

205
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,080
But if I wanted to survive,

206
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:16,210
I had to depend on the Empress Dowager—

207
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:17,200
just like how you are

208
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,460
using Xia Jingyan now.

209
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:20,710
Eventually,

210
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,670
driven by despair and revenge,

211
00:12:22,670 --> 00:12:24,330
you'll follow in my footsteps

212
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,480
and become like me.

213
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:29,020
I've never been a good person,

214
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:30,800
but you are

215
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:33,610
the kindest person I've ever met.

216
00:12:34,870 --> 00:12:35,870
Let go of all this.

217
00:12:36,150 --> 00:12:37,150
Let go of revenge.

218
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:38,350
Live a peaceful life.

219
00:12:38,500 --> 00:12:39,740
It's not too late.

220
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,200
Xia Jingshi,

221
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:50,200
I've already fallen into the abyss,

222
00:12:51,110 --> 00:12:52,770
and only now do you offer help.

223
00:12:54,130 --> 00:12:55,730
I won't be grateful for this.

224
00:12:56,870 --> 00:12:58,870
I only find it even more disgusting!

225
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:01,000
You might as well not help me at all.

226
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,620
Just be the villain you are.

227
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,550
You've made me what I am today,

228
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:05,240
and now you want to save me?

229
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:06,720
You think I'm pitiful, don't you?

230
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:08,250
I don't need your sympathy!

231
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,800
You don't deserve it!

232
00:13:14,550 --> 00:13:15,810
Since that's the case,

233
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:17,680
so be it.

234
00:13:17,750 --> 00:13:18,750
Princess Xiyang,

235
00:13:19,470 --> 00:13:21,840
His Majesty said you've been gone
for a while picking flowers,

236
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:23,370
so he sent me to check on you.

237
00:13:25,630 --> 00:13:26,760
An enemy is an enemy.

238
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:30,380
Next time, don't pretend to be concerned

239
00:13:30,670 --> 00:13:32,200
or convince me to turn back.

240
00:13:33,350 --> 00:13:34,240
You just think killing me

241
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:36,100
would interfere with your plans.

242
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:39,130
Xia Jingshi,

243
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:41,840
no one knows better than I do

244
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:43,270
what's on your mind

245
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:46,500
in this very moment.

246
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:15,120
What's wrong with you?

247
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:17,490
Do you still want this job?

248
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:32,790
First Prince?

249
00:14:33,870 --> 00:14:34,210
You…

250
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:36,400
you're still alive.

251
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:41,010
I didn't see anything.

252
00:14:41,010 --> 00:14:42,120
I didn't see anything.

253
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,810
I know nothing!

254
00:14:44,630 --> 00:14:45,800
You know nothing?

255
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:49,720
Then there's no need for you to live.

256
00:14:50,870 --> 00:14:51,940
I'm still useful.

257
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,380
I'm still useful!

258
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:56,970
Your Highness, please don't kill me.

259
00:14:57,320 --> 00:14:58,600
What do you need me to do?

260
00:14:58,600 --> 00:15:00,390
I will do whatever you ask.

261
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:04,630
[Personal Guards: Li Jianxin,
Zhao Yunhai, Zhang Moying]

262
00:15:03,390 --> 00:15:04,650
Just as you predicted,

263
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:05,670
the Empress Dowager

264
00:15:05,670 --> 00:15:07,510
really did plant spies among Xia Jingyan's

265
00:15:07,510 --> 00:15:08,510
personal guards.

266
00:15:09,790 --> 00:15:11,080
That's just how she is.

267
00:15:12,150 --> 00:15:13,320
She has to

268
00:15:13,670 --> 00:15:14,240
have everything

269
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,750
under her control.

270
00:15:16,790 --> 00:15:19,190
The Royal Guards
protect the imperial palace.

271
00:15:19,190 --> 00:15:21,320
Military Commander Liang Pin was her man.

272
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:23,650
The personal guards protect Xia Jingyan.

273
00:15:23,790 --> 00:15:25,840
So naturally,
she has her people there too.

274
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:27,700
She wants to control everything.

275
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:30,770
Yet Your Highness has seen through it all.

276
00:15:30,790 --> 00:15:32,650
They're digging their own grave.

277
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,720
Where did this list come from?

278
00:15:35,030 --> 00:15:36,490
Wang Encheng provided it.

279
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:37,720
Among the personal guards,

280
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:39,480
there's a team leader named Zhang Ming.

281
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:41,320
He's close to Wang Encheng.

282
00:15:40,330 --> 00:15:43,480
[Personal Guards: Zhu Tieyi,
Chen Shuangjian, Zhong Jingsong]

283
00:15:41,750 --> 00:15:43,200
Zhang Ming told him in private

284
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:45,000
that these particular personal guards

285
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:46,080
had reported secretly

286
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:47,810
to the Empress Dowager before.

287
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:50,370
Does Zhang Ming know

288
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:52,080
Wang Encheng is

289
00:15:52,120 --> 00:15:53,380
investigating for us?

290
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:54,760
Rest assured.

291
00:15:55,270 --> 00:15:57,000
Wang Encheng is tight-lipped.

292
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:59,400
He's never mentioned his connection to us.

293
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:01,220
Your Highness,

294
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:03,000
did you request this list

295
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:04,310
because you

296
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:05,510
already have a plan?

297
00:16:07,040 --> 00:16:08,800
This is a gift for Xia Jingyan.

298
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:12,870
There's already a rift between Xia Jingyan
and the Empress Dowager,

299
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:14,000
but they haven't

300
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:15,530
completely fallen out yet.

301
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:17,030
So I'm going to

302
00:16:17,030 --> 00:16:18,100
fan the flames.

303
00:16:20,670 --> 00:16:21,520
Find a way

304
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:23,570
to get this list to Xia Jingyan.

305
00:16:23,910 --> 00:16:24,710
Just make sure

306
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,390
no one realizes

307
00:16:26,390 --> 00:16:27,220
it's from us.

308
00:16:27,630 --> 00:16:28,080
Yes.

309
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:34,690
What did you say?

310
00:16:35,150 --> 00:16:36,330
I really did

311
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:37,970
meet with the First Prince.

312
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:40,390
He wishes to meet with you in private.

313
00:16:40,390 --> 00:16:41,470
Given the urgency,

314
00:16:41,550 --> 00:16:42,360
I had no choice

315
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:43,660
but to agree

316
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:46,260
to relay the message to you first.

317
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:48,000
Please forgive me.

318
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,360
You did well.

319
00:16:54,790 --> 00:16:55,590
Your Majesty,

320
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:58,210
are you going to meet him?

321
00:16:58,480 --> 00:16:59,080
Of course.

322
00:16:59,630 --> 00:17:00,490
Why wouldn't I?

323
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:04,760
You're my confidant.

324
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,540
Speak freely.

325
00:17:06,870 --> 00:17:09,589
Then, allow me to be frank.

326
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:11,720
Prime Minister Zhuang died

327
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:13,250
at the First Prince's hand.

328
00:17:13,349 --> 00:17:14,000
If that

329
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,310
hadn't happened,

330
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:16,440
the throne

331
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:18,050
would have

332
00:17:18,829 --> 00:17:19,760
belonged to him.

333
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:24,770
I've spoken out of turn.

334
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:26,550
Please forgive me.

335
00:17:27,589 --> 00:17:29,250
You've only spoken the truth.

336
00:17:29,349 --> 00:17:30,550
There's nothing to forgive.

337
00:17:30,550 --> 00:17:31,000
Get up.

338
00:17:35,350 --> 00:17:36,320
But I believe

339
00:17:36,830 --> 00:17:37,430
Suige

340
00:17:37,470 --> 00:17:38,760
would never harm me.

341
00:17:39,270 --> 00:17:40,510
Go make arrangements immediately.

342
00:17:40,510 --> 00:17:41,710
I'll set out tonight.

343
00:17:42,270 --> 00:17:42,960
But you must

344
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:44,030
not tell anyone.

345
00:17:44,490 --> 00:17:45,890
This must remain secret,

346
00:17:46,110 --> 00:17:47,640
especially from my mother.

347
00:17:49,550 --> 00:17:50,960
Yes, Your Majesty.

348
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:57,470
Minister Shen.

349
00:17:58,830 --> 00:18:00,890
I've been watching you for some time.

350
00:18:01,070 --> 00:18:01,920
You met His Majesty

351
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:03,450
in private again and again.

352
00:18:03,550 --> 00:18:05,010
You seem to be in a hurry.

353
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:06,540
What is it about?

354
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:10,340
Just official business.

355
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:17,240
You understand

356
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:18,470
which way the wind blows.

357
00:18:18,470 --> 00:18:19,860
Don't be misled into choosing

358
00:18:19,860 --> 00:18:20,720
the wrong side.

359
00:18:23,110 --> 00:18:24,440
I'm giving you one last chance

360
00:18:24,440 --> 00:18:25,760
to tell the truth.

361
00:18:28,550 --> 00:18:29,350
What?

362
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:31,180
It's absolutely true.

363
00:18:31,510 --> 00:18:32,350
The men we placed

364
00:18:32,350 --> 00:18:34,080
among the personal guards

365
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:36,560
were just executed by His Majesty's order.

366
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:39,070
How did His Majesty discover them?

367
00:18:39,070 --> 00:18:40,810
I secretly looked into it.

368
00:18:41,480 --> 00:18:42,600
It's said that

369
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:45,240
after His Majesty
killed Military Commander Liang,

370
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:47,220
he searched his residence

371
00:18:47,550 --> 00:18:49,330
and found that list.

372
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,350
Nonsense!

373
00:18:51,070 --> 00:18:53,350
Liang Pin had nothing
to do with the personal guards.

374
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:54,400
How would he know?

375
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,070
Liang Pin is now dead.

376
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:58,500
Dead men tell no tales.

377
00:18:59,030 --> 00:19:00,350
No one will ever know

378
00:19:00,790 --> 00:19:02,590
where that list really came from.

379
00:19:02,590 --> 00:19:03,530
I doubt

380
00:19:04,200 --> 00:19:06,130
His Majesty had any real evidence,

381
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:08,460
but he had them executed all the same.

382
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:11,270
When does His Majesty

383
00:19:11,270 --> 00:19:13,200
ever need evidence to kill anyone?

384
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:17,010
Summon the Prince of Zhennan to see me.

385
00:19:17,590 --> 00:19:18,240
Yes.

386
00:19:36,450 --> 00:19:38,090
[Yangyue Palace, Yuxiu Palace,
Hehuan Hall]

387
00:19:38,440 --> 00:19:40,170
Are you troubled by something?

388
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:41,680
Come, come.

389
00:19:42,310 --> 00:19:43,550
I thought all you did was play around

390
00:19:43,550 --> 00:19:45,410
without a care for state affairs.

391
00:19:45,550 --> 00:19:46,000
But you're

392
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:47,730
actually diligent sometimes.

393
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:51,500
State affairs?

394
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:53,000
What state affairs?

395
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:53,590
If I had to

396
00:19:53,590 --> 00:19:55,200
handle state affairs myself,

397
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:55,920
then what's the point

398
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:57,650
of paying all those officials?

399
00:19:58,070 --> 00:19:58,510
Come.

400
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:00,270
Sit.

401
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:03,040
Look at this.

402
00:20:03,260 --> 00:20:04,420
[Jiyue Hall, Linhua Palace,
Pixiang Hall, Shuhua Palace]

403
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:04,240
I ordered the palace staff

404
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:05,590
to pick some new residences for you:

405
00:20:05,590 --> 00:20:08,120
Jiyue Hall, Linhua Palace,
and Pixiang Hall.

406
00:20:09,350 --> 00:20:10,750
I have no idea

407
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:12,210
which one you'd prefer.

408
00:20:12,590 --> 00:20:13,450
How about this?

409
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:14,500
You take a look.

410
00:20:14,590 --> 00:20:16,120
Choose whichever you like.

411
00:20:16,720 --> 00:20:18,510
So this is what you were studying?

412
00:20:18,510 --> 00:20:19,110
Yes.

413
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:20,850
If you like them all,

414
00:20:21,070 --> 00:20:22,160
I'll give them all to you.

415
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,200
I guess a few

416
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:23,920
pedantic old officials

417
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:24,920
will object.

418
00:20:25,160 --> 00:20:26,090
But don't worry.

419
00:20:26,440 --> 00:20:27,440
Whoever dares to object,

420
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:28,590
I'll have them beheaded.

421
00:20:28,590 --> 00:20:30,190
I don't need a new residence.

422
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:32,100
I can just stay in the Mirror Room.

423
00:20:32,790 --> 00:20:34,590
The Mirror Room is too shabby.

424
00:20:34,590 --> 00:20:35,790
Just a place to sleep!

425
00:20:36,270 --> 00:20:37,000
If you ask me,

426
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:38,000
the Mirror Room is no different

427
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,330
from all these palaces.

428
00:20:42,030 --> 00:20:43,070
Feng Xiyang!

429
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:44,680
I have so many palaces,

430
00:20:44,680 --> 00:20:46,340
and you don't like any of them?

431
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:49,500
If you continue to be so unappreciative…

432
00:20:52,530 --> 00:20:53,750
I'll build you a new palace.

433
00:20:53,750 --> 00:20:54,610
How about that?

434
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:56,420
Xia Jingyan,

435
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:58,680
instead of thinking about these things,

436
00:20:58,680 --> 00:20:59,350
why don't you help me figure out

437
00:20:59,350 --> 00:21:01,410
how to kill the Murong father and son?

438
00:21:02,160 --> 00:21:03,090
What's the rush?

439
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:05,240
Once they're killed

440
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:06,590
and you get your revenge,

441
00:21:06,590 --> 00:21:07,820
you'll want to leave.

442
00:21:09,680 --> 00:21:11,410
You want to go back on your word?

443
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:12,720
You're the ruler of a kingdom.

444
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:13,640
A king's word is law.

445
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:15,570
You can't break your promise to me!

446
00:21:15,830 --> 00:21:17,340
I am a ruler, that's true,

447
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:18,570
but I'm also a man.

448
00:21:19,240 --> 00:21:20,570
Isn't it normal for a man

449
00:21:20,790 --> 00:21:21,680
to lie to a woman?

450
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:22,200
You…

451
00:21:25,170 --> 00:21:25,920
Wait, wait.

452
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:28,000
Don't get upset.

453
00:21:28,240 --> 00:21:29,700
I was just joking with you.

454
00:21:30,310 --> 00:21:31,240
Alright.

455
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:33,270
I never lie to women,

456
00:21:33,550 --> 00:21:34,810
especially not to you.

457
00:21:35,070 --> 00:21:36,530
It was you who used that...

458
00:21:36,790 --> 00:21:37,510
that bet

459
00:21:37,510 --> 00:21:39,160
to stop me from attacking Susha.

460
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:40,350
You have to give me some time

461
00:21:40,350 --> 00:21:41,680
to come up with a new plan

462
00:21:41,790 --> 00:21:43,650
to kill the Murong father and son.

463
00:21:43,720 --> 00:21:45,200
Alright. Be patient.

464
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:46,780
You just want me to stay.

465
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:47,720
You want this imperial palace

466
00:21:47,720 --> 00:21:48,800
to become my cage!

467
00:21:49,110 --> 00:21:49,720
Your cage?

468
00:21:51,440 --> 00:21:52,440
What a great idea!

469
00:21:52,590 --> 00:21:54,050
Why didn't I think of that?

470
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:54,680
I'll immediately

471
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:55,640
build you a new palace

472
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:56,550
that looks like a cage!

473
00:21:56,550 --> 00:21:57,280
You're sick!

474
00:21:58,440 --> 00:21:59,310
Don't go yet!

475
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:00,830
I have a gift for you.

476
00:22:05,290 --> 00:22:06,950
[Fuxin Pavilion]

477
00:22:10,790 --> 00:22:13,050
I asked you to kill the Princess of Susha,

478
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:14,860
yet you still haven't done it.

479
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:16,390
You've really let me down.

480
00:22:17,270 --> 00:22:18,400
Forgive me, Mother.

481
00:22:19,830 --> 00:22:21,040
His Majesty has

482
00:22:21,350 --> 00:22:22,400
assigned personal guards

483
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:23,260
to protect her.

484
00:22:24,070 --> 00:22:26,000
I really haven't found the chance.

485
00:22:26,030 --> 00:22:26,820
Mother,

486
00:22:27,360 --> 00:22:29,610
could you temporarily

487
00:22:29,960 --> 00:22:31,820
remove the personal guards

488
00:22:32,270 --> 00:22:33,110
so that I can…

489
00:22:33,110 --> 00:22:35,100
I only gave you this one task,

490
00:22:35,550 --> 00:22:37,350
and you still need my help?

491
00:22:41,510 --> 00:22:42,570
Calm down, Mother.

492
00:22:42,960 --> 00:22:44,420
Forgive my incompetence.

493
00:22:46,510 --> 00:22:47,200
Forget it.

494
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:49,960
You have the will but lack the means.

495
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:50,640
After all, this is

496
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:51,970
not your Pingling City.

497
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:56,100
It's Mother's Pingling City.

498
00:22:56,550 --> 00:22:58,010
I was away for so many years

499
00:22:58,480 --> 00:23:00,240
guarding Pingling for you.

500
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:03,770
All land under heaven
belongs to the Emperor.

501
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:06,130
It's His Majesty's Pingling City.

502
00:23:06,510 --> 00:23:08,240
You weren't guarding it for me.

503
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:10,070
Don't say such foolish words

504
00:23:10,070 --> 00:23:11,110
ever again.

505
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:13,110
Get up.

506
00:23:18,830 --> 00:23:20,000
His Majesty has become

507
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,750
increasingly difficult to understand.

508
00:23:21,750 --> 00:23:23,880
Officials proposed attacking Susha,

509
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:25,200
but he refused.

510
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:27,680
It must be Feng Xiyang interfering.

511
00:23:28,310 --> 00:23:30,030
I planned to restore

512
00:23:30,030 --> 00:23:31,360
your military command,

513
00:23:31,830 --> 00:23:33,630
but it keeps getting postponed.

514
00:23:33,830 --> 00:23:35,560
After all these years outside,

515
00:23:36,350 --> 00:23:37,200
being able to return

516
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:39,130
and serve you with filial devotion

517
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:40,750
isn't such a bad thing.

518
00:23:41,790 --> 00:23:43,590
Rather than a filial son,

519
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:45,400
what I truly need

520
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:47,930
is the Prince of Zhennan
who lets me rest easy.

521
00:23:49,350 --> 00:23:51,000
Mother, you mean...

522
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:53,880
You fool,

523
00:23:54,680 --> 00:23:57,140
you're in real danger
without realizing it.

524
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:59,110
His Majesty has always wanted you dead.

525
00:23:59,110 --> 00:24:00,970
In the past, I could hold him back,

526
00:24:01,550 --> 00:24:02,240
but now,

527
00:24:02,270 --> 00:24:04,470
with Feng Xiyang messing with his mind,

528
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:05,400
he barely even

529
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:07,130
acknowledges me as his mother.

530
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:09,110
If he ever insists on killing you,

531
00:24:09,110 --> 00:24:10,640
I may not be able to stop him.

532
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:12,900
Please enlighten me, Mother.

533
00:24:13,070 --> 00:24:14,720
How can I protect myself?

534
00:24:15,850 --> 00:24:18,200
Right now,
with peace between the two kingdoms,

535
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:19,660
he thinks you're useless.

536
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:23,100
But when war breaks out,
it'll be different.

537
00:24:23,200 --> 00:24:25,350
That's why Feng Xiyang must die,

538
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:27,030
and Susa must be attacked.

539
00:24:28,070 --> 00:24:29,160
However, I don't want

540
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:30,030
this matter

541
00:24:30,590 --> 00:24:32,990
to create a rift
between His Majesty and me.

542
00:24:33,310 --> 00:24:34,110
I understand.

543
00:24:35,400 --> 00:24:37,350
I'll first kill Feng Xiyang

544
00:24:37,590 --> 00:24:38,920
and frame Susha for it.

545
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:40,510
Then I'll provoke His Majesty

546
00:24:40,510 --> 00:24:42,240
into waging war against Susha.

547
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:45,270
Since I can't go after

548
00:24:45,590 --> 00:24:47,070
Feng Xiyang in the palace,

549
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:48,780
I might as well…

550
00:24:51,550 --> 00:24:53,030
try something outside.

551
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:54,590
How could His Majesty

552
00:24:54,590 --> 00:24:56,480
possibly let her leave the palace?

553
00:24:56,480 --> 00:24:58,280
The opportunity will come soon.

554
00:24:59,550 --> 00:25:00,110
Mother,

555
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:04,330
the Qianqiu Festival is approaching.

556
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:27,100
Will your brother stand with you?

557
00:25:29,460 --> 00:25:30,480
Chengyang and I

558
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:33,220
may not be brothers from the same mother,

559
00:25:33,440 --> 00:25:34,350
but I watched him grow up

560
00:25:34,350 --> 00:25:35,590
all these years.

561
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:37,150
I've always treated him

562
00:25:37,150 --> 00:25:38,690
like my own brother.

563
00:25:39,350 --> 00:25:40,940
I know his character well.

564
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:43,570
He might be completely in the dark,

565
00:25:43,720 --> 00:25:45,030
unaware of the truth,

566
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:47,550
believing what his mother has told him.

567
00:25:47,550 --> 00:25:48,200
No matter

568
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:49,750
what Empress Zhuang told him,

569
00:25:49,750 --> 00:25:51,470
it must be full of loopholes.

570
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:52,920
In such a just world,

571
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:55,050
no one can truly turn black into white.

572
00:25:56,030 --> 00:25:58,090
Chengyang can tell right from wrong.

573
00:25:58,240 --> 00:25:59,030
I trust him.

574
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:02,680
Although I've never met Feng Chengyang,

575
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:04,440
after hearing what you've said,

576
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:05,070
he sounds like

577
00:26:05,070 --> 00:26:06,270
a reasonable person.

578
00:26:06,740 --> 00:26:08,670
To maintain a kind heart,

579
00:26:09,000 --> 00:26:11,000
even with blood ties to the Zhuangs—

580
00:26:11,310 --> 00:26:12,640
that's really not easy.

581
00:26:14,270 --> 00:26:15,640
I was worried

582
00:26:15,680 --> 00:26:17,940
that you brothers would become enemies.

583
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:19,000
So many royal siblings

584
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:20,200
like you would fight

585
00:26:21,030 --> 00:26:21,960
to the bitter end

586
00:26:22,030 --> 00:26:23,300
for the throne.

587
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:24,820
Surprisingly,

588
00:26:25,110 --> 00:26:26,980
you two are the opposite.

589
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:28,540
That's truly rare.

590
00:26:29,310 --> 00:26:31,030
If it weren't for the throne,

591
00:26:32,500 --> 00:26:33,750
my buddies like Gu Yu

592
00:26:34,240 --> 00:26:36,100
wouldn't have ended up like that.

593
00:26:41,030 --> 00:26:43,230
You are the most important person to me.

594
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:45,260
After everything,

595
00:26:46,110 --> 00:26:47,570
I still have you by my side,

596
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:50,240
and Lu Ke, Yun Fang, and Yun Qing,

597
00:26:50,510 --> 00:26:51,590
who are not blood relatives

598
00:26:51,590 --> 00:26:52,920
but are more than family,

599
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:53,590
by my side.

600
00:26:54,480 --> 00:26:55,940
I'm already very content.

601
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:08,060
I didn't expect

602
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:10,310
His Highness to suffer so much

603
00:27:10,310 --> 00:27:11,570
in the Storm Alliance.

604
00:27:12,030 --> 00:27:13,030
Thankfully, Miss Yixiao was

605
00:27:13,030 --> 00:27:14,490
by his side through it all,

606
00:27:14,550 --> 00:27:15,240
pulling His Highness

607
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:16,840
back from the brink of death.

608
00:27:16,960 --> 00:27:18,420
Let's not talk about that.

609
00:27:19,350 --> 00:27:20,070
How are you?

610
00:27:21,110 --> 00:27:22,510
Let me see if it's healed.

611
00:27:23,220 --> 00:27:24,830
Just superficial wounds.
They're all healed.

612
00:27:24,830 --> 00:27:25,440
Don't bother.

613
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:26,640
Why are you acting shy like a girl?

614
00:27:26,640 --> 00:27:27,550
Just let me check.

615
00:27:27,550 --> 00:27:28,590
What's wrong with you?

616
00:27:28,590 --> 00:27:29,790
You wanna fight?

617
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:30,920
Never mind.

618
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:32,110
I won't fight you.

619
00:27:32,110 --> 00:27:33,270
You're still recovering

620
00:27:33,270 --> 00:27:34,200
from your injuries.

621
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:35,080
If I beat you,

622
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:36,590
it wouldn't be honorable.

623
00:27:36,590 --> 00:27:37,750
You beat me?

624
00:27:38,510 --> 00:27:39,790
Have you ever beaten me?

625
00:27:39,790 --> 00:27:41,650
Have I ever fought you seriously?

626
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:44,550
Didn't I kill

627
00:27:44,550 --> 00:27:45,310
20 more enemies than you

628
00:27:45,310 --> 00:27:46,030
on the battlefield?

629
00:27:46,030 --> 00:27:47,750
Fine, fine.

630
00:27:47,750 --> 00:27:49,010
You're the best, okay?

631
00:27:49,750 --> 00:27:50,550
Just you wait.

632
00:27:51,030 --> 00:27:51,790
After I avenge His Highness

633
00:27:51,790 --> 00:27:53,120
by killing the Murongs,

634
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,160
we can

635
00:27:54,160 --> 00:27:55,290
have a proper match.

636
00:27:55,920 --> 00:27:56,510
I'll always be

637
00:27:56,510 --> 00:27:57,880
one step ahead of you on the battlefield.

638
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:58,480
Fine.

639
00:27:59,200 --> 00:28:00,090
I'd like to see

640
00:28:00,350 --> 00:28:02,080
who will really come out on top.

641
00:28:02,110 --> 00:28:02,960
It's a deal then.

642
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:03,620
It's a deal.

643
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:16,720
This is a bow
with a draw weight of over two piculs.

644
00:28:16,720 --> 00:28:17,350
Yes.

645
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:19,680
I thought Your Highness had died

646
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:20,680
and planned to assassinate the Murongs

647
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:21,730
to avenge you.

648
00:28:22,110 --> 00:28:22,750
But they always have

649
00:28:22,750 --> 00:28:24,070
guards protecting them.

650
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:25,350
I can only shoot

651
00:28:25,350 --> 00:28:26,480
from 150 paces away.

652
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:28,860
At that distance,

653
00:28:29,310 --> 00:28:31,170
you can hit six or seven out of ten.

654
00:28:32,310 --> 00:28:33,830
They're both military commanders.

655
00:28:33,830 --> 00:28:35,630
They wear armor when they go out.

656
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:36,680
From 150 paces away,

657
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:38,200
a kill shot is extremely difficult.

658
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:40,130
At best, you could hit a vital spot.

659
00:28:40,270 --> 00:28:41,590
But regular bows and arrows

660
00:28:41,590 --> 00:28:42,750
can't penetrate armor

661
00:28:42,750 --> 00:28:43,890
even if you hit,

662
00:28:44,350 --> 00:28:45,110
so you have to use

663
00:28:45,110 --> 00:28:46,830
a heavy-tipped arrow and a strong bow.

664
00:28:46,830 --> 00:28:47,350
Yes.

665
00:28:48,030 --> 00:28:48,830
A few days ago,

666
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:50,210
I secretly got this bow.

667
00:28:50,350 --> 00:28:51,240
If my brother found out,

668
00:28:51,240 --> 00:28:52,880
he'd stop me from taking risks,

669
00:28:52,880 --> 00:28:54,480
so I kept it stashed outside.

670
00:28:54,480 --> 00:28:55,240
However, I've only

671
00:28:55,240 --> 00:28:56,700
ever used a two-picul bow,

672
00:28:56,830 --> 00:28:57,960
so I can't guarantee

673
00:28:57,960 --> 00:28:59,350
a kill shot with this one.

674
00:28:59,350 --> 00:29:00,070
I can try it.

675
00:29:00,310 --> 00:29:01,750
The Moon-Shooting Bow I used before

676
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:03,000
had a draw weight of over two piculs.

677
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:03,480
No.

678
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:06,140
Lord Ling said

679
00:29:06,510 --> 00:29:07,920
you can't draw a strong bow.

680
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:09,520
I've completely recovered.

681
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:10,790
Look.

682
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:15,710
Yixiao.

683
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:17,390
With this bow,

684
00:29:17,550 --> 00:29:18,880
I can lend you a hand

685
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:20,790
and help you deal with the Murongs.

686
00:29:20,790 --> 00:29:22,270
But if you hurt yourself again

687
00:29:22,270 --> 00:29:23,640
just to kill them,

688
00:29:23,880 --> 00:29:25,270
it's simply not worth it.

689
00:29:25,270 --> 00:29:26,150
Don't worry,

690
00:29:26,270 --> 00:29:27,240
I know my limits.

691
00:29:27,830 --> 00:29:28,630
Don't forget,

692
00:29:29,110 --> 00:29:30,440
I'm Fu Yixiao after all.

693
00:29:37,680 --> 00:29:38,540
Mind your step.

694
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:48,960
Someone's coming.

695
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:49,480
These are

696
00:29:49,480 --> 00:29:50,610
Song's scout bells.

697
00:29:50,720 --> 00:29:51,920
Once someone gets near this area,

698
00:29:51,920 --> 00:29:52,890
the bells will be

699
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:54,020
triggered to ring.

700
00:29:56,030 --> 00:29:56,640
Your Highness,

701
00:29:56,640 --> 00:29:57,510
someone is coming this way

702
00:29:57,510 --> 00:29:58,270
with guards.

703
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:00,370
It's Chengyang.

704
00:30:08,830 --> 00:30:10,290
Greetings, Your Majesty.

705
00:30:17,310 --> 00:30:18,030
Your Majesty,

706
00:30:18,030 --> 00:30:19,310
I'll wait outside

707
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:20,240
for you.

708
00:30:57,440 --> 00:30:58,240
Who are you?

709
00:30:58,830 --> 00:31:01,030
Your brother is waiting for you inside.

710
00:31:38,390 --> 00:31:39,390
Let me see

711
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:42,720
what Chengyang looks like

712
00:31:43,240 --> 00:31:44,200
as an emperor.

713
00:31:45,070 --> 00:31:45,680
Suige,

714
00:31:46,800 --> 00:31:48,040
it's so wonderful

715
00:31:48,550 --> 00:31:49,480
to see you again.

716
00:31:49,830 --> 00:31:51,360
You also thought I was dead?

717
00:31:53,030 --> 00:31:54,550
In the past, every time you returned

718
00:31:54,550 --> 00:31:55,880
from a victorious campaign,

719
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:57,210
I'd go welcome you back.

720
00:31:57,750 --> 00:31:59,590
Once, you didn't come back with the army.

721
00:31:59,590 --> 00:32:01,190
They said you died in battle.

722
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:02,240
I was devastated.

723
00:32:03,350 --> 00:32:04,400
Later, I told you

724
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:06,600
that unless you saw my body,

725
00:32:06,750 --> 00:32:08,010
you shouldn't believe

726
00:32:08,030 --> 00:32:09,360
any rumors from anyone.

727
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:10,840
Because your brother

728
00:32:11,030 --> 00:32:12,630
is the invincible God of War.

729
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,500
Murong Yao said

730
00:32:15,790 --> 00:32:17,270
your body was left in the wilderness

731
00:32:17,270 --> 00:32:18,530
and couldn't be found.

732
00:32:18,720 --> 00:32:20,400
I didn't see it with my own eyes,

733
00:32:20,400 --> 00:32:21,660
so I didn't believe it.

734
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:23,720
Come.

735
00:32:24,310 --> 00:32:24,880
Sit.

736
00:32:34,240 --> 00:32:34,880
Brother,

737
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:36,670
actually,

738
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:38,570
ascending to the throne

739
00:32:39,110 --> 00:32:39,970
was not my wish.

740
00:32:40,310 --> 00:32:40,960
I know.

741
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:42,480
I already learned about

742
00:32:42,480 --> 00:32:43,440
what happened between you

743
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:45,040
and Grandfather in the past.

744
00:32:45,070 --> 00:32:45,590
Suige,

745
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:48,130
why didn't you tell me?

746
00:32:48,750 --> 00:32:50,790
Telling you would only have worried you

747
00:32:50,790 --> 00:32:51,640
needlessly.

748
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:54,310
There's a perpetrator for every injustice.

749
00:32:54,310 --> 00:32:55,880
None of this should have come

750
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:57,440
between us brothers.

751
00:32:58,050 --> 00:32:59,310
Why trouble yourself?

752
00:33:03,070 --> 00:33:03,730
Chengyang,

753
00:33:04,720 --> 00:33:05,270
I've heard

754
00:33:05,270 --> 00:33:06,880
you've been secretly investigating

755
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:08,510
the truth behind Father's assassination.

756
00:33:08,510 --> 00:33:10,840
The fact
that you came to see me today means

757
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:11,750
that you still

758
00:33:11,750 --> 00:33:13,410
care about me as your brother.

759
00:33:13,750 --> 00:33:14,350
Brother,

760
00:33:15,550 --> 00:33:17,110
how did Father really die?

761
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,640
And who set you up?

762
00:33:21,100 --> 00:33:22,560
The Murong father and son.

763
00:33:24,280 --> 00:33:25,680
They forged an imperial edict

764
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:27,140
to lure me into the palace.

765
00:33:29,070 --> 00:33:30,400
By the time I saw Father,

766
00:33:31,440 --> 00:33:32,970
he had already passed away.

767
00:33:37,430 --> 00:33:38,690
Who else was involved?

768
00:33:39,750 --> 00:33:40,880
An event this big…

769
00:33:41,750 --> 00:33:43,030
I don't believe the Murongs did it

770
00:33:43,030 --> 00:33:44,400
all on their own.

771
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:46,680
You're asking me this…

772
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:50,790
because you already

773
00:33:50,790 --> 00:33:52,050
have an answer, right?

774
00:33:52,790 --> 00:33:53,440
Brother,

775
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:58,570
I want to hear it from you directly.

776
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:00,980
Was my mother involved

777
00:34:02,640 --> 00:34:04,480
in the attempt to murder you?

778
00:34:16,550 --> 00:34:17,480
I have no proof,

779
00:34:19,670 --> 00:34:21,840
but she must have been involved.

780
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:24,630
Chengyang,

781
00:34:25,710 --> 00:34:26,969
I called you here today

782
00:34:27,510 --> 00:34:28,030
because I hope

783
00:34:28,030 --> 00:34:30,000
you can prepare yourself in advance.

784
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:31,840
And I hope you can understand me.

785
00:34:33,550 --> 00:34:35,080
Because what I'm about to do

786
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:37,929
is to kill my enemies with my own hands.

787
00:34:39,550 --> 00:34:40,230
Brother,

788
00:34:41,630 --> 00:34:43,290
I'll return the throne to you.

789
00:34:43,590 --> 00:34:45,480
But may I ask you one thing?

790
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:47,730
Spare my mother.

791
00:34:49,030 --> 00:34:50,760
I will take her away from Yujing

792
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:51,929
and never come back.

793
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:54,460
I'm the only family

794
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:56,880
my mother has now.

795
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:02,110
All her mistakes were for my sake.

796
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:05,320
Her sins are my sins.

797
00:35:07,030 --> 00:35:08,560
Let me pay the price for her.

798
00:35:08,920 --> 00:35:10,320
What have you done wrong?

799
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:14,590
You and I are merely

800
00:35:14,590 --> 00:35:15,990
pawns of circumstances.

801
00:35:26,710 --> 00:35:27,370
Chengyang.

802
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:34,550
I promise you:

803
00:35:36,710 --> 00:35:38,400
I will not kill your mother.

804
00:35:44,070 --> 00:35:45,130
Qianqiu Festival?

805
00:35:46,230 --> 00:35:48,230
Xia Jingyan's Daily Chronicle says

806
00:35:48,670 --> 00:35:50,280
that every year at the Qianqiu Festival,

807
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:52,920
he leaves the palace
to visit his ancestral home.

808
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:54,120
If we want to kill him,

809
00:35:54,510 --> 00:35:55,840
that's the best chance.

810
00:35:56,670 --> 00:35:57,590
But for such occasions,

811
00:35:57,590 --> 00:35:59,050
security is always tight.

812
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:00,960
There will be countless guards
protecting him,

813
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:02,420
both openly and secretly.

814
00:36:02,510 --> 00:36:04,960
That's why we need
to use the Empress Dowager.

815
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:06,670
When Xia Jingyan leaves the palace,

816
00:36:06,670 --> 00:36:09,060
he'll certainly bring
Feng Xiyang with him.

817
00:36:09,060 --> 00:36:10,000
No one wants Feng Xiyang dead

818
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:11,730
more than the Empress Dowager.

819
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:13,030
She will secretly

820
00:36:13,510 --> 00:36:14,960
help us reassign most of

821
00:36:14,960 --> 00:36:16,320
Xia Jingyan's guards.

822
00:36:17,110 --> 00:36:18,170
If that's the case,

823
00:36:18,670 --> 00:36:19,590
our chances of success

824
00:36:19,590 --> 00:36:20,790
will be much greater.

825
00:36:21,190 --> 00:36:22,840
But will the Empress Dowager agree?

826
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:24,070
She definitely will.

827
00:36:25,400 --> 00:36:26,440
She's eager

828
00:36:26,440 --> 00:36:28,760
to provoke a war between the two kingdoms.

829
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:29,480
Only then

830
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:32,290
will Xia Jingyan
need to rely on her again.

831
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,980
We need to prepare in advance.

832
00:36:37,430 --> 00:36:39,480
It's time to send word to Pingling City

833
00:36:39,480 --> 00:36:40,810
and call in more people.

834
00:36:41,110 --> 00:36:41,840
Understood.

835
00:36:44,880 --> 00:36:45,940
What are you doing?

836
00:36:46,960 --> 00:36:47,710
Prince of Zhennan,

837
00:36:47,710 --> 00:36:49,110
His Majesty summons you.

838
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:09,120
You're angry?

839
00:37:12,650 --> 00:37:13,510
Who's the fool

840
00:37:13,510 --> 00:37:14,910
that upset Her Highness?

841
00:37:21,510 --> 00:37:23,040
It couldn't be me, could it?

842
00:37:25,190 --> 00:37:26,510
Why would I be angry?

843
00:37:27,510 --> 00:37:28,240
Xia Jingyan,

844
00:37:28,510 --> 00:37:29,440
don't think I can't

845
00:37:29,440 --> 00:37:30,900
take revenge without you.

846
00:37:32,630 --> 00:37:33,430
Interesting.

847
00:37:33,510 --> 00:37:34,480
Then tell me,

848
00:37:34,480 --> 00:37:35,110
what's your plan?

849
00:37:35,110 --> 00:37:35,590
Did you

850
00:37:35,590 --> 00:37:36,990
just come here to mock me?

851
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:44,070
I came to help you.

852
00:37:44,550 --> 00:37:45,070
Get out.

853
00:37:47,030 --> 00:37:48,630
The more ungrateful you are,

854
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:49,980
the more I like you.

855
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:51,090
Bring him in!

856
00:37:59,710 --> 00:38:01,200
Why did you bring him here?

857
00:38:01,550 --> 00:38:02,810
I don't want to see him!

858
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:12,460
Greetings, Your Majesty.

859
00:38:12,480 --> 00:38:13,400
May I ask why

860
00:38:13,590 --> 00:38:14,720
you've summoned me?

861
00:38:17,710 --> 00:38:19,340
You tried to kill my woman,

862
00:38:19,760 --> 00:38:22,160
and you still don't know
why I summoned you?

863
00:38:25,100 --> 00:38:26,830
Your Majesty, what do you mean?

864
00:38:27,320 --> 00:38:28,450
I don't understand.

865
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:32,400
You forgot quite quickly.

