Why did you

867
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:36,080
go to the Flower Hall?

868
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:37,400
You've been visiting

869
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:39,260
the Empress Dowager repeatedly.

870
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:39,880
What task did

871
00:38:39,880 --> 00:38:40,760
she assign you?

872
00:38:41,480 --> 00:38:42,810
The same as Liang Pin's?

873
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:43,580
To kill her?

874
00:38:48,440 --> 00:38:49,280
I was merely paying

875
00:38:49,280 --> 00:38:51,740
my regular respects
to the Empress Dowager.

876
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:53,560
Still won't admit it?

877
00:38:54,030 --> 00:38:54,550
Good.

878
00:38:55,230 --> 00:38:57,280
You pay your respects more often
than I do.

879
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:58,140
You're filial.

880
00:38:58,320 --> 00:38:59,000
I'm not.

881
00:38:59,670 --> 00:39:00,870
Is that what you mean?

882
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:01,840
You misunderstand.

883
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:02,590
Then what were you doing

884
00:39:02,590 --> 00:39:03,650
at the Flower Hall?

885
00:39:03,840 --> 00:39:06,040
Were you perhaps rekindling a romance?

886
00:39:09,550 --> 00:39:10,110
I...

887
00:39:10,190 --> 00:39:11,880
Think carefully about your answer.

888
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:12,960
If you were rekindling a romance

889
00:39:12,960 --> 00:39:13,760
with my woman,

890
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:15,090
I'd be very displeased.

891
00:39:15,230 --> 00:39:16,210
If not,

892
00:39:16,440 --> 00:39:18,040
I'd be even more displeased.

893
00:39:18,220 --> 00:39:20,220
You don't find my woman attractive?

894
00:39:26,670 --> 00:39:27,940
If I'm displeased,

895
00:39:28,210 --> 00:39:29,670
someone's head will roll.

896
00:39:31,160 --> 00:39:31,830
Tell me.

897
00:39:32,150 --> 00:39:33,150
Tell me, why did you go to her?

898
00:39:33,150 --> 00:39:34,750
Was it to rekindle a romance?

899
00:39:35,570 --> 00:39:37,420
If you want me dead, Your Majesty,

900
00:39:37,420 --> 00:39:39,280
why bother with finding excuses?

901
00:39:41,370 --> 00:39:42,710
Who do you think you are?

902
00:39:44,200 --> 00:39:45,860
Do I need an excuse to kill you?

903
00:39:46,800 --> 00:39:47,360
At the Flower Hall,

904
00:39:47,360 --> 00:39:48,960
I had something to say to him.

905
00:39:55,630 --> 00:39:57,710
Prince of Zhennan, have you forgotten?

906
00:39:57,710 --> 00:40:00,310
I was the one who stopped you
at the Flower Hall.

907
00:40:00,360 --> 00:40:01,930
I asked if you had ever,

908
00:40:02,550 --> 00:40:03,320
even for a moment,

909
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:04,880
imagined growing old with me.

910
00:40:04,880 --> 00:40:05,280
I...

911
00:40:06,550 --> 00:40:06,960
You...

912
00:40:07,440 --> 00:40:08,840
You were rekindling a romance with him?

913
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:10,070
Don't say that again!

914
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:11,480
He and I broke ties long ago.

915
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:12,610
There's no romance!

916
00:40:13,400 --> 00:40:14,070
I just

917
00:40:14,070 --> 00:40:15,620
wanted an answer.

918
00:40:16,360 --> 00:40:17,560
What was your answer?

919
00:40:23,440 --> 00:40:24,190
Never.

920
00:40:25,080 --> 00:40:26,900
♪ Roaming freely ♪

921
00:40:27,240 --> 00:40:30,500
♪ Unafraid of wind or frost ♪

922
00:40:30,920 --> 00:40:31,550
I see.

923
00:40:32,480 --> 00:40:34,390
♪ The wet wings ♪

924
00:40:34,660 --> 00:40:38,020
♪ Will carry me far away ♪

925
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:42,360
You crazy woman,

926
00:40:41,890 --> 00:40:45,570
♪ Don't cry, don't cry ♪

927
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:43,070
are you serious?

928
00:40:43,070 --> 00:40:44,190
Xia Jingyan, I've told you,

929
00:40:44,190 --> 00:40:44,840
I can still get my revenge

930
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:46,230
without you!

931
00:40:46,280 --> 00:40:47,220
Let go of me!

932
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:48,070
Let me kill him!

933
00:40:48,070 --> 00:40:49,190
-Take him away! Now!
-Let me kill him!

934
00:40:48,100 --> 00:40:52,920
♪ I'll remember the way home ♪

935
00:40:50,590 --> 00:40:51,660
Xia Jingshi,

936
00:40:51,710 --> 00:40:52,800
I'll kill you!

937
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:56,400
Listen to me!

938
00:40:57,280 --> 00:40:58,340
You're from Susha.

939
00:40:58,440 --> 00:40:59,320
If you kill him,

940
00:40:59,630 --> 00:41:01,070
his followers won't let you go,

941
00:41:01,070 --> 00:41:02,320
nor will the people of Jinxiu!

942
00:41:02,320 --> 00:41:03,330
Then why did you

943
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:04,500
bring him to see me?

944
00:41:04,630 --> 00:41:05,800
I just wanted to humiliate him

945
00:41:05,800 --> 00:41:07,590
and scare him a bit
to make you feel better!

946
00:41:07,590 --> 00:41:08,390
Xia Jingyan,

947
00:41:08,590 --> 00:41:09,480
remember this:

948
00:41:09,760 --> 00:41:10,320
I was

949
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:11,920
never joking about revenge.

950
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:13,920
If you dare toy with me again,

951
00:41:14,400 --> 00:41:15,590
I won't let you off!

952
00:41:18,880 --> 00:41:19,800
You crazy woman.

953
00:41:19,800 --> 00:41:20,730
What did you say?

954
00:41:21,670 --> 00:41:22,870
I said I'll remember!

955
00:41:51,990 --> 00:41:53,450
You've seen your brother,

956
00:41:53,760 --> 00:41:55,490
but why are you even more upset?

957
00:41:57,360 --> 00:41:58,560
He came to see me today

958
00:41:59,110 --> 00:42:01,240
because he cares for me as his brother.

959
00:42:01,710 --> 00:42:03,400
But I told him terrible news.

960
00:42:04,110 --> 00:42:06,310
Chengyang has already lost his father.

961
00:42:06,400 --> 00:42:07,190
How will he face

962
00:42:07,190 --> 00:42:08,670
his mother from now on?

963
00:42:13,760 --> 00:42:15,290
Usually at times like this,

964
00:42:15,960 --> 00:42:16,800
wouldn't you offer me

965
00:42:16,800 --> 00:42:17,800
words of comfort?

966
00:42:18,880 --> 00:42:20,480
Why are you silent this time?

967
00:42:20,630 --> 00:42:21,760
I was just thinking:

968
00:42:22,710 --> 00:42:23,670
how can there be someone

969
00:42:23,670 --> 00:42:25,200
as kind as you in this world?

970
00:42:25,630 --> 00:42:26,440
His mother

971
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:28,170
caused you to lose your mother,

972
00:42:28,480 --> 00:42:30,210
yet you're still worried about

973
00:42:30,440 --> 00:42:31,070
how he will

974
00:42:31,070 --> 00:42:32,530
get along with his mother.

975
00:42:36,480 --> 00:42:38,210
After all you've been through,

976
00:42:38,440 --> 00:42:39,400
I'm really glad

977
00:42:39,840 --> 00:42:41,480
you still have a younger brother
like Chengyang.

